nodes.text: This cloned individual served as a pilot in the Sky Battle of Quell and operated a Consular-class cruiser.

This pilot was part of Jedi Master Anakin Skywalker's rescue team to save Master Aayla Secura and the remaining clone troopers inside her flagship the Liberty. The clone pilot died when multiple Vulture droids fired at the ship and had shot the clone, causing him to hit the hyperdrive button, which resulted in the ship going to hyperspace.
